PrecisAppointment of PAUL E. KENNEDY of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Chairman of the Royal Canadian Mounted Police Public Complaints Commission, on an interim basis, to hold office during good behaviour until 12 months after the conclusion of both the factual inquiry and the policy review by the Honourable Dennis R.
